1 A RESOLUTION
2 To commend Justin Wax for being named the 2026 Principal of the Year in Louisiana.
3 WHEREAS, it is most fitting to recognize Justin Wax for his dedication to the
4 students of Denham Springs Junior High School and to commend him for being named the
5 2026 Principal of the Year; and
6 WHEREAS, Principal Wax currently serves in his fourth year as principal of
7 Denham Springs Junior High School; under his leadership, the school was recognized as a
8 2024 Top Gains Honoree and featured in U.S. News and World Report's Best Middle
9 Schools in 2024 and 2025; and
10 WHEREAS, Principal Wax is a leader in student advocacy; he has taken innovative
11 steps to address teen vaping by offering educational alternatives to suspension and facilitated
12 the installation of campus vape detection technology; and
13 WHEREAS, Principal Wax spoke before the House Committee on Judiciary and
14 effectively advocated to raise the minimum age requirements for the purchase of vaping
15 products; and
16 WHEREAS, Principal Wax is dedicated to STEM education and has pioneered an
17 aquaponics lab that provides hands-on opportunities to conserve endangered plant species
18 in Louisiana and teaches sustainable produce cultivation; and
19 WHEREAS, Principal Wax is committed to addressing students' needs and has
20 partnered with community leaders to eliminate student fees and ensure access for
